    "address_gaps": "Options A and B are insufficient. While aspiration and compression are important, they don't address the underlying deficiency. Option C is premature \u2013 attempting aspiration without factor VIII replacement will likely result in re-bleeding and further cartilage damage. Option E is incorrect as there *are* appropriate therapeutic options.",
